    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Congratulations on Completing Your Training Program!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
        <p>Congratulations on successfully completing the
          {{program}}
          <strong>{{programName}}</strong>! Training. Your dedication, hard
          work, and enthusiasm throughout this training have been truly
          commendable.</p>
        <p>We are proud to recognize your achievement and are excited to see how
          you will apply the skills and knowledge you've gained in your future
          endeavors. Attached to this email, you will find your
          <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>, which serves as a
          testament to your commitment and accomplishment.</p>
        <p>Please donâ€™t hesitate to reach out if you have any questions or need
          further assistance as you continue to grow and succeed.</p>
        <p>We also encourage you to celebrate this achievement by sharing your
          certificate on your social media platforms like
          <strong>LinkedIn, X (formerly Twitter), and Instagram</strong>.
          Inspire your network by letting them know about your accomplishment!</p>
        <p>Once again, congratulations on this milestone! We look forward to
          seeing the great things you will achieve.</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p><strong>{{senderName}}</strong><br />{{senderPosition}}<br
          />{{organizationName}}<br />{{contactInfo}}</p>
      </div>
      {{! <div class="footer">
      <p>Attachment: Certificate of Completion</p>
    </div> }}
    </div>
  </body>
</html>